Battlecode (MIT 6.470) package manager.

USAGE

Install the Battlecode distribution. Later, use the same command to update the distribution.

   bcpm dist
   
Check out a player repository and set it up for development.

   bcpm install git@git.pwnb.us:six370/team989.git


INSTALLATION

On Ubuntu:
   
    sudo apt-get install ruby-full rubygems
    sudo gem install rubygems-update
    sudo `gem env | grep 'EXECUTABLE DIRECTORY' | ruby -e "puts gets.split(': ', 2).last"`/update_rubygems

On both OSX and Ubuntu:
   
    sudo gem install echoe flexmock
    git clone git@git.pwnb.us:six370/bcpm
    rake install
